graph LR
    Notebooks[Notebooks Component<br/>Workbench Images]

    subgraph "External Dependencies (Required)"
        UBI9[UBI9 Python 3.12<br/>registry.access.redhat.com]
        JupyterLab[JupyterLab 4.4<br/>PyPI package]
        OpenShiftCLI[OpenShift CLI oc<br/>mirror.openshift.com]
        Pandoc[Pandoc<br/>Document conversion]
        TexLive[TeX Live<br/>LaTeX rendering]
    end

    subgraph "External Dependencies (GPU - Optional)"
        CUDA[CUDA Base Images<br/>12.6/12.8/13.0]
        ROCM[ROCM Base Images<br/>6.2/6.3/6.4]
    end

    subgraph "External Dependencies (IDE-specific)"
        RStudio[RStudio Server<br/>R IDE]
        CodeServer[code-server<br/>VS Code in browser]
    end

    subgraph "External Dependencies (ML Frameworks - Optional)"
        PyTorch[PyTorch 2.x<br/>Deep learning]
        TensorFlow[TensorFlow 2.x<br/>Deep learning]
    end

    subgraph "Internal RHOAI Dependencies"
        NotebookController[odh-notebook-controller<br/>Operator - deploys workbenches]
        Dashboard[odh-dashboard<br/>UI - displays images]
        KubeflowPipelines[kubeflow-pipelines<br/>Elyra integration]
        OAuthProxy[oauth-proxy<br/>Authentication sidecar]
        PVC[Persistent Volume Claims<br/>User data storage]
        Routes[OpenShift Routes<br/>HTTP ingress]
    end

    subgraph "External Services (Runtime)"
        PyPI[pypi.org<br/>Python packages]
        QuayIO[quay.io<br/>Image registry]
        RedHatRegistry[registry.redhat.io<br/>RHEL images]
        S3Storage[S3 Storage<br/>Model artifacts]
        GitRepos[Git Repositories<br/>Code repos]
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>Cluster management]
    end

    subgraph "Build Infrastructure"
        Konflux[Konflux CI/CD<br/>Tekton pipelines]
    end

    %% Core dependencies
    Notebooks -->|base OS runtime| UBI9
    Notebooks -->|IDE framework| JupyterLab
    Notebooks -->|cluster tools| OpenShiftCLI
    Notebooks -->|doc conversion| Pandoc
    Notebooks -->|PDF export| TexLive

    %% GPU dependencies
    Notebooks -.->|GPU acceleration| CUDA
    Notebooks -.->|AMD GPU| ROCM

    %% IDE dependencies
    Notebooks -.->|R IDE images| RStudio
    Notebooks -.->|VS Code images| CodeServer

    %% ML frameworks
    Notebooks -.->|PyTorch images| PyTorch
    Notebooks -.->|TensorFlow images| TensorFlow

    %% Internal integrations
    NotebookController -->|deploys workbenches using| Notebooks
    Dashboard -->|displays available| Notebooks
    KubeflowPipelines -->|launches runtime images| Notebooks
    OAuthProxy -->|protects workbench access| Notebooks
    Notebooks -->|requires| PVC
    Notebooks -->|requires| Routes

    %% Runtime services (from workbench)
    Notebooks -->|installs packages| PyPI
    Notebooks -->|pulls images| QuayIO
    Notebooks -->|pulls base images| RedHatRegistry
    Notebooks -->|reads/writes data| S3Storage
    Notebooks -->|clones/pushes code| GitRepos
    Notebooks -->|kubectl/oc commands| K8sAPI

    %% Build process
    Konflux -->|builds and publishes| Notebooks
    Konflux -->|pulls from| UBI9
    Konflux -->|pulls from| CUDA
    Konflux -->|pulls from| ROCM
    Konflux -->|pushes to| QuayIO
    Konflux -->|pushes to| RedHatRegistry

